Another plug for the *only* VW repair shop I have ever had good experiences 
with.  I had my ball joints replaced at Meyers Foreign in Las Vegas, 
NV.  If it is within 500 miles of you, I would make the trip to have them 
do the job.  The price was very fair and they did top notch work.

-David

